# Project Context

**Single source of truth:** `.docs/CONTEXT.md`

At the start of every conversation — and before answering questions about this project's stack, architecture, conventions, or communication style — read `.docs/CONTEXT.md` and follow it.

That file defines:

- Project overview and tech stack
- Architecture and documentation map
- Behavioral guidelines
- Communication protocol (ADHD-optimized)
